Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.93,0:00:08.28,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know without a doubt \Nthat I killed [*].
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.86,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing will change that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:15.14,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I decided \Nto come clean here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:18.51,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is my confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.53,0:00:21.56,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been two weeks since the trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:25.76,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and nobody remembers [*] \Never being in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.82,0:00:28.62,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's been completely forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:33.99,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only I, the sole person deeply involved \Nin his death, still remember [*].
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:38.50,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I get the feeling it's \Nonly a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:42.77,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why, while my \Nmemory is still clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.24,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:48.48,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and how to stop the calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:50.98,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:52.61,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Send them back to death, \Nwhere they belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:55.28,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Send the dead back to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:01:00.58,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how to stop the \Ncalamity once it's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.83,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Back in elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:38.01,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,there was a girl who \Nlooked just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.49,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:41.99,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.91,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought Misaki was an only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.50,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't in the same class as her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.93,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,but I know people called her Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:51.96,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,That makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.05,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,From her address,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:56.49,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,she shouldn't have even been \Nin the same school as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:59.78,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why it's so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:05.33,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Did she wear an eyepatch \Nover her left eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.37,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:13.01,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Our Misaki lost her eye when she was four!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:16.03,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then she...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:42.15,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is the dead person here on this trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.66,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,The extra person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:52.38,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,...is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.29,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:00.51,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.63,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:06.12,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might have \Ndone something bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.14,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Teshigawara? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:14.31,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you two a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:16.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.58,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know a kid named Tomohiko Kazami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:21.90,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.39,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:27.67,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Kazami? What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:29.35,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:32.23,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,He's a class officer and the guy \Nyou've always been stuck with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.32,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:36.14,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,How could I not know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:43.48,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad... Really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.59,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:48.67,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might have been wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.74,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:55.00,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:58.44,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure he was the extra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.15,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,So just now, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.74,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,He was...? You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.09,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Kazami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:06.82,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:08.70,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.45,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:14.21,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I lie about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.58,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to probe him a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.54,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,since he's been acting weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:25.33,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,And he said he didn't remember \Nthe stuff we did together as kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.43,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't remember much \Nfrom elementary school, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:29.95,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:33.06,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I braced myself, and asked him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.56,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,"You're not really Kazami, are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:39.31,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,"You're the extra person \Nin the class, aren't you?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:44.69,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,He looked panicked at first, \Nthen he flew into a rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.03,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,He was acting so suspiciously, \NI was sure it was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:53.92,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,So like the tape said, if he died, \Nif he "returned to death,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:55.76,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,we'd all be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:58.37,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,...you killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.63,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:06.41,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:10.39,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,We started grappling and ended \Nup outside, on the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.30,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,And the next thing I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:16.27,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,He was lying still on the ground below.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.66,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Blood was coming from his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.94,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I got scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:24.65,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,and ran back down the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:28.51,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I'd seen Sakaki come in here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:33.27,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,So you wanted to find out \Nif Kazami was the extra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.92,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.25,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, if the extra died,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:40.87,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be as if he'd never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.99,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,But you two said you know him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.53,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,so I must've been wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.84,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Sakaki, was I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:54.29,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Either that, or he's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.15,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:58.72,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Falling from two stories up \Nwouldn't necessarily kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.11,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see where he fell from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.37,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,It's past that row of shrubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:18.53,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing we should \Ndo is check if he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.02,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.29,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Maejima?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.32,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.18,Default,Maejima,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.50,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:16.43,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Were you stabbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:19.84,Default,Maejima,0000,0000,0000,,I looked... in the dining hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.67,Default,Maejima,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:23.98,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:50.09,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Maejima, we've gotta get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:52.72,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you screaming, Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.74,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.41,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.55,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Maejima!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.44,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,He's hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.18,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:01.83,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,He's been stabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.56,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a fire in the dining hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.14,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.89,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The manager's inside, dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.13,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,He was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The killer must've started the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.23,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.03,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.23,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find Kazami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.74,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:23.62,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.75,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Was that Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.16,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sugiura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.66,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You, get Maejima someplace safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:34.18,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,and call 119!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.17,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.07,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,That room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:54.57,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine, and Takako's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.91,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako, are you in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:05.23,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:07.79,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako, where are you? Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:12.74,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.14,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:18.16,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Sugiura or Kazami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:20.05,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Kazami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:24.42,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,He came to my room, covered with mud \Nand his face clouded in anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:26.68,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,saying Teshigawara was acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:27.43,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.30,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I asked what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.15,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,but he just glared daggers at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.75,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,So I mentioned the tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.47,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You told him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:36.59,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:41.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,He's not in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.45,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.83,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,The tape recorder's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.60,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.00,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Sakaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.25,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kazami here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.63,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,How's Maejima?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.39,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I left him with someone who heard \Nthe screams and ran in to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.31,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:02.39,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:07.98,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and look for Kazami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:11.28,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,And stop by all the rooms \Nand tell everyone to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.19,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,There's a fire! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.37,Default,Ouji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.07,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:20.81,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,A killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:22.74,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:26.60,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, there's a fire in the dining hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.08,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,and we don't know where Kazami went.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.82,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's so messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.63,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,We have to tell Ms. Mikami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.34,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Mikami? Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:43.86,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:49.52,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.27,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is that blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.44,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:01.36,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't suppose something \Nhappened to Ms. Mikami, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:06.58,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think we should go \Noutside and call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.83,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.40,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Not before we make sure Ms. Mikami is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.81,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Mikami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.23,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.41,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Teshigawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.49,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,And Mochizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:54.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It came from downstairs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.18,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.48,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:19.48,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:21.10,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.38,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.03,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,If you had died, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.57,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.12,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you can't live without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:33.64,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.92,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Send the dead back to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.26,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.89,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Teshigawara! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.31,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,M-My leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.78,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Send the dead back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.13,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.38,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:29.23,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "Send the dead back to death."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.39,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,How did she know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:35.14,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,She listened to the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:39.19,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You found it in the old \Nclass 3 homeroom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.24,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ogura told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.20,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're looking for a clue \Nto stopping the calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.70,Default,Ogura,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:49.27,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.47,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The tape was brought here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.92,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, by Mochizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.69,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,As the head of countermeasures, \NI had to listen to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.44,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But why does she think \NMisaki is the dead person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.89,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since our trip to the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.62,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako's been emotionally unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.51,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.07,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, Akazawa! \NIt's too dangerous to go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:17.07,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important message \Nfrom the head of countermeasures
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.60,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,to the students of class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:22.01,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,The tape you are about to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:26.73,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,was left behind 15 years ago, \Nwhen the calamity stopped midyear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:36.43,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and how to stop the calamity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:38.41,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:40.33,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Send them back to death, \Nwhere they belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:43.21,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Send the dead back to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:48.45,Default,Matsunaga,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how to stop the \Ncalamity once it's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.34,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,These are the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.39,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,The calamity was stopped \Nmidyear 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:59.77,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,And the dead person this year is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.02,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Mei Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:08.70,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,I know this because we went \Nto the same elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.53,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,and her left eye was intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:14.79,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Yet now, she is missing her left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.29,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:22.40,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,That she was reborn incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.74,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,The Mei Misaki we know is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.37,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why we must...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:33.01,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,...kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.31,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.19,Default,Tsujii,0000,0000,0000,,Return the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.36,Default,Kawahori,0000,0000,0000,,...to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.27,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Return the dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:57.89,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.13,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Mikami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.33,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill your own classmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.21,Default,Tsujii,0000,0000,0000,,But if we send the dead \Nperson back to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.10,Default,Tsujii,0000,0000,0000,,no one else will have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.61,Default,Kawahori,0000,0000,0000,,If we kill Misaki, \Nthe calamity will end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:11.55,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.86,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do this! You're making a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:16.99,Default,Kawahori,0000,0000,0000,,Then who the hell's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:18.89,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.55,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.04,Default,Tsujii,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.69,Default,Tsujii,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:27.69,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:44.53,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.29,Default,Kawahori,0000,0000,0000,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:01.55,Default,Matsui,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:02.51,Default,Watanabe,0000,0000,0000,,The dead girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:05.22,Default,Ogura,0000,0000,0000,,I'll avenge my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:05.97,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.03,Default,Ogura,0000,0000,0000,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:08.90,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.40,Default,Kawahori,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:18.44,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.08,Default,Ogura,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:35.22,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, it's slippery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.46,Default,Ogura,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:47.18,Default,Ogura,0000,0000,0000,,Send the dead back to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.20,Default,Kawahori,0000,0000,0000,,Ogura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:05.70,Default,Tsujii,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:14.96,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're sav—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.68,Default,Kawahori,0000,0000,0000,,Go in from downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.55,Default,Ouji,0000,0000,0000,,You really think it's Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:32.81,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,There's something off about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:34.27,Default,Ouji,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:40.86,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:43.45,Default,Ouji,0000,0000,0000,,He did say there was a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:46.04,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any flames, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.41,Default,Saruta,0000,0000,0000,,The dining hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:54.29,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,We should be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.84,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.77,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:27.43,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion in the \Ndining hall, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:28.84,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:33.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Maejima passed out in front \Nof the dining hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:35.79,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Could Sugiura have...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:36.92,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.97,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably that old crone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.07,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Crone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:52.23,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.57,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,...are in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:58.02,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't kill you, \Nsince you're not the dead one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.98,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Izumi seems fond of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:12.79,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Send the dead back to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:16.77,Default,Sugiura,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:52.93,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:21:57.00,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.43,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.32,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Akazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:05.63,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:10.64,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Takako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:16.14,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mei... Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:18.72,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:20.22,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, Akazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.22,0:22:21.77,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sugiura was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:24.44,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.62,0:22:27.70,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,If the dead person was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:35.98,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,all of these tragic \Nthings would stop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:45.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:48.88,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:22:55.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.89,0:24:40.07,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by oneself.
